title: Gatta Alla Pari, Just like a Cat

sources.title: Gatta Alla Pari, Just like a Cat
sources.description: From IMDb: Baby Ryan (Malu) gains access to James's (Antonio Zequilla) household and accepts the job as an au pair girl. She is holding a dark secret and carefully plans her revenge on James who is oblivious of her true identity. ___________ I don't have subtitles for this one but somehow the IMDb description makes the movie seem more ambitious than it looks. Lots of nudity and 90's softcore sex.
